WEBVTT

NOTE
Audio Description captions for the FF8 intro FMV.
Timestamps were fit by analyzing the provided MP4 (scene-cut + keyframe alignment).
If you use a different game version/encode, you may need small timing nudges.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.000
Fade in from black. Ocean surf comes into view.

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:27.000
Waves roll onto a smooth, pale beach.

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:33.800
Over the ocean, the words appear: "Why...?"

00:00:33.800 --> 00:00:37.800
The view races forward; the word "waiting..." streaks across the water.

00:00:37.800 --> 00:00:48.400
The ocean becomes a cracked, sunlit desert. The words read: "for what?"

00:00:48.400 --> 00:00:52.400
Rinoa stands with her back to us in a field of flowers. Text: "If you come here..."

00:00:52.400 --> 00:00:55.500
Rinoa in the flower field. Text: "You'll find me."

00:00:55.500 --> 00:01:01.600
Close on Rinoa's hand as pink petals drift past; she opens her palm.

00:01:01.600 --> 00:01:08.600
Petals swirl. A white feather appears, glowing softly, then lifts away.

00:01:08.600 --> 00:01:28.000
The feather rises into dark storm clouds as petals whirl around it.

00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:32.000
Title card: "SQUARESOFT presents."

00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:36.600
A gunblade drops and slams into rock; a black-gloved hand grips it.

00:01:36.600 --> 00:01:46.000
White feathers flood the screen—rapid flashes of faces and motion.

00:01:46.000 --> 00:01:51.600
Edea appears in an ornate horned headdress; Rinoa turns amid blowing feathers.

00:01:51.600 --> 00:01:59.000
Feathers fade into a stormy sky as the scene shifts toward a rocky battlefield.

00:01:59.000 --> 00:02:04.800
Seifer, blond and smirking, swings his gunblade in a sweeping arc.

00:02:04.800 --> 00:02:10.400
Seifer faces Squall and lifts a hand, beckoning—taunting him to come closer.

00:02:10.400 --> 00:02:18.000
Wide shot: Squall and Seifer rush together; blades crash and sparks burst.

00:02:18.000 --> 00:02:22.200
Rapid intercuts: Edea's face, Rinoa's gaze, then the duel again.

00:02:22.200 --> 00:02:26.600
Close-up: the two gunblades lock; metal grinds as they strain against each other.

00:02:26.600 --> 00:02:34.600
Seifer presses the attack; Squall recoils and turns, jaw clenched.

00:02:34.600 --> 00:02:39.800
Seifer thrusts out his hand—orange fire magic erupts in a blast.

00:02:39.800 --> 00:02:46.000
Squall lies on the rocky ground, grimacing as he tries to rise.

00:02:46.000 --> 00:02:56.600
Montage: Rinoa's pendant at her throat; Edea's eyes; Rinoa reaching through swirling feathers.

00:02:56.600 --> 00:02:59.600
Warm-toned overlays: Rinoa and Edea superimposed in quick flashes.

00:02:59.600 --> 00:03:03.600
Rinoa and Squall step toward each other against a bright, glowing sky.

00:03:03.600 --> 00:03:05.400
They embrace. The image cuts to black.

00:03:05.400 --> 00:03:12.447
The Final Fantasy VIII logo appears.
